-#
  /questions/:id/edit — single-question paper-is-editor (Wave 5).
  Left pane: the question rendered as editable paper (same partial the
  Canvas tab uses). Right rail: content / marking / metadata, driven by
  QuestionTypes registry. Classic multi-section form stays at ?ui=classic.
- if params[:ui] == 'classic'
  = render 'classic_edit'
- else
  = render 'paper_edit'
